# Building kompott backend  

## Installing 3rdparty dependencies  

### Installing erlang (https://github.com/yrashk/kerl). 

  $ curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spawngrid/kerl/master/kerl
  $ chmod +x kerl 
  $ ./kerl build R16B03-1 r16b03-1
  $ sudo mkdir /opt/kompott 
  $ sudo chown USERNAME /opt/kompott 
  $ ./kerl install r16b03-1 /opt/kompott/3rdparty/erlang-r16b03-1
  $ cd /opt/kompott/3rdparty 
  $ ln -s /opt/kompott/3rdparty/erlang-r16b03-1 erlang 

### Installing rebar 

  $ mkdir /opt/kompott/3rdparty/bin 
  $ cd /opt/kompott/3rdparty/bin 
  $ curl -O https://raw.github.com/wiki/rebar/rebar/rebar 
  $ chmod +x rebar
 
## Setting up build environment and building the release  

  $ . /opt/kompott/3rdparty/erlang/activate 
  $ export PATH=/opt/kompott/3rdparty/bin:$PATH 

  
  



